<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?><image-reference id="_7b02c52a-a04d-4d4b-a16e-d6f9fc94c47d"><num>13.2.7 (explanatory)</num><title id="_bc088ff8-76ee-4d30-80ec-fbed6654796a">Attached Class 10a building examples</title><image alt="Attached Class 10a building examples." href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/13-2-7-explanatory-attached-class-10a-building-examples.svg"/><desc-note id="_639210fd-6973-4cf3-bfe9-14eac53e827e"><p>In (a), the thermal performance <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/1432_4.0.0.xml#_af6fde9f-147d-4782-8b85-42044e80fd42" id="_d7fc2aba-4204-45fa-8389-0e73775a35f4" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">required</xref> for the Class 1 building may be achieved by including the walls and floor of the Class 1 building that adjoin the Class 10a garage.</p><p>In (b), the thermal performance <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/1432_4.0.0.xml#_af6fde9f-147d-4782-8b85-42044e80fd42" id="_6447fb14-70ae-4a7b-8e3b-0767523f8cf3" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">required</xref> for the Class 1 building may be achieved by including the outside walls and floor of the Class 10a garage.</p></desc-note></image-reference>